Rammsund, both the greatest new-norvegian rockband and the greatest tribute band in Norway are ready for new adventures. Together with Aleksander Vinter, aka Vinter In Hollywood, they started the project Staal. We're talking about heavy industrial metal with new-norwegian lyrics. What you get is beautiful, heavy and intimidating music with balls of steel!
